      <para id="id1170498292246">You must add to the list!</para>
      <para id="id1170498280673">[LO 6.1.4]</para>
      <para id="id1170496846977">SHAKE THE WHIP!!</para>
      <para id="id1170502395315">Try these! </para>
      <para id="id1170506144441">Remember to study the word.</para>
      <para id="id1170498810449">Cover it up!</para>
      <para id="id1170494557250">Try to spell it! </para>
      <para id="id1170502317978">Write it.</para>
      <para id="id1170496995385">Check your word!</para>
      <para id="id1170500341146">These words are missing their first letters – solve the mystery!</para>
      <table id="id1170506536714" summary="">
        <tgroup cols="3">
