      <para id="id1170500690986">Challenge!! How many of these words can you fit into a nonsense sentence?</para>
      <para id="id1170498622519"/>
      <para id="id1170501057990">Fill in the missing words to complete the rhymes:</para>
      <para id="id1170496888416">To reach the coffee on the ___stand on tiptoe and stretch yourself!</para>
      <para id="id1170502718596">I'm so ____ I need a drink. Water tastes awful, so I ___!</para>
      <para id="id1170498060355">Little Bo Beep has lost her sheep – ___ would they be fast asleep?</para>
      <para id="id1170496845703">___ and lightning makes me quiver. I get so scared I start to ___ .</para>
